INITIALIZATION.

START-OF-SELECTION.

  DATA: l_name TYPE c LENGTH 10,
        l_text TYPE string.

  CONCATENATE 'hello World' l_name INTO l_text.

  WRITE: / l_text.

*  l_text = 'Hello'.
*  l_text = l_name.

  l_text = replace( val = l_text
                    sub = 'World'
                    with = 'Fausto' ).

  WRITE: / l_text.
